{"tid":1682430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要請義士睇TVB!","createTime":"2019-10-30T04:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T04:53:40.000Z","uid":272017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"20851c08d7912fa27e27a8fee12d54100bd25d1b","tid":1682430,"uid":272017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:53:31.000Z","msg":"[自認標題黨，預左比人吊。]<br />\n廢材前特首日日MON 住蘋果，鬧爆在上高賣廣告的店舖。<br />\nMON POST 狗睇連登來刺探手足的動作。<br />\n<br />\n我想說，我們總要有人看看TVB。<br />\n1. 看看有哪些店舖在TVB 落廣告，上去相關店家的社交平台洗板。並考慮把把那些屢勸不聽的店加入罷買藍店行列。<br />\n2. 睇睇佢幾時出外景，齊齊洗板。<br />\n3. 佢出外景時出手表達訴求"},{"pid":"00f5ead89b11a91044e208ae80a7714932503e19","tid":1682430,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}